    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Tamás Nádasdy (Prague, 21 February 1549)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">The last time they had the opportunity to talk with
                            Nádasdy and Pál Várday about the oversight of the counties on this side
                            of the Danube was at the last Bratislava diet. They are hurrying to the
                            lords of the Chamber so he can get the money collected through the tax
                            collectors to Nádasdy. Because the King now really needs all the money
                            he can get, he asks Nádasdy not to find it difficult to have the taxes
                            collected in the territories he oversees on this side of the Danube and
                            give it to Wolfgang Kremer or Christoph Linck. Since they have the 10
                            denarii, he has written to the councillors of the Chamber to send the
                            county register to Nádasdy.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Spectabilis et Magnifice Domine, et Amice nobis Observandissime, <choice>
                        <orig>s<gap extent="1" reason="damage" unit="word"/>tem</orig>
                        <supplied>s<corr>alu</corr>tem</supplied>
                    </choice> et obsequiorum nostrorum commendationem! </p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Recordamur <choice>
                        <orig>Sp<gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/>em</orig>
                        <supplied>Sp<corr>ectabil</corr>em</supplied>
                    </choice> et Magnificam Dominationem Vestram credimus eius subsidii, quod ex <choice>
                        <orig>d<gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/></orig>
                        <supplied>d<corr>uo</corr></supplied>
                    </choice> denorum nummorum a dominis regnicolis et <choice>
                        <orig>sta<gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/>bus</orig>
                        <supplied>sta<corr>ti</corr>bus</supplied>
                    </choice> in proxima congregatione Posoniensi<note type="critic" xml:id="note.1"
                        >The diet began on 16 October, 1548.</note> nobis in <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/>um</orig>
                        <supplied><corr>…</corr>um</supplied>
                    </choice> sustentationem proxime oblatum est. Tunc temporis fueramus (uti
                    recordamur) super ea re unacum reverendissimo domino
                        <persName>archiepiscopo</persName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.2">Pál
                        Várday.</note> etc. Spectabili Magnificae Dominationi Vestrae locuti, ut
                    eadem huius nostri oblati subsidii, in comitatibus <choice>
                        <orig>Cis<gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/>bium</orig>
                        <supplied>Cis<corr>danu</corr>bium</supplied>
                    </choice> habitis curam diligentem gerere. Servitii <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/></orig>
                        <supplied><corr>in</corr></supplied>
                    </choice> intuitu vellet, et dominos similiter camerarios <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/>ramus</orig>
                        <supplied><corr>prope</corr>ramus</supplied>
                    </choice>, quo per dicatores taxam denorum <choice>
                        <orig>n<gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/>morum</orig>
                        <supplied>n<corr>um</corr>morum</supplied>
                    </choice> manibus Spectabilis Magnificae Dominationis Vestrae suo tempore <choice>
                        <orig>f<gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/>liter</orig>
                        <supplied>f<corr>ide</corr>liter</supplied>
                    </choice> administrari curarent. Nam nobis circa regiam maiestatem <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/>tibus</orig>
                        <supplied><corr>praesen</corr>tibus</supplied>
                    </choice> magnis sumptibus opus est, proinde iterum <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="unknown" reason="damage" unit="word"/>umque</orig>
                        <supplied><corr>iter</corr>umque</supplied>
                    </choice> petimus Dominationem Vestram Magnificam, ne gravetur intuitu amicitiae
                    nostrae et servitiorum praedictum subsidium in vicinis sibi comitatibus,
                    Cisdanubium habitis diligenter et absque defectu aliquali exigi facere,
                    exactumque secundum registrum dicatorum et ad manus suas acceptum aut ad nos
                    nacta commoditate ubicumque Dei voluntate erimus mittere, aut si id fieri non
                    posset, ad manus sive <persName>Kremmer</persName>,<note type="critic"
                        xml:id="note.3">Wolfgang Kremer.</note> sive <persName>Lynk</persName><note
                        type="critic" xml:id="note.4">Christoph Linck was a <hi rend="italic"
                            >factor</hi> in Vienna and Steward, see <hi rend="smallcap">Sarusi
                            Kiss</hi> 2009; and <hi rend="smallcap">Gecsényi</hi> 2010,
                        15.</note><placeName>Viennae</placeName> assignari facere, qui nobis illud
                    facile administrabunt. Quo vero haec decem nummorum pecunia rectius et sine
                    damno exigi possit, scripsimus ad dominos consiliarios camerae, ut regestrum
                    comitatuum, ex quibus deni illi nummi exigi debebant, ad Spectabilem Magnificam
                    Dominationem Vestram mittant. Quod illos facere non diffidimus. Quicquid studii
                    ac diligentiae hac in re eadem nobis praestiterit, nos idipsum omni genere
                    amicitiae, et obsequiorum <milestone unit="pb"/>promereri apud Spectabilem
                    Magnificam Dominationem Vestram studebimus, quam in reliquo optamus
                    val&lt;ere&gt; felicissimam.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3"><placeName>Pragae</placeName> 21. Februarii anno Domini 1549.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Frater et servitor Agriensis etc. manu
                            propria.</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.5">Spectabili et magnifico domino Thomae de Nadasd comiti perpetuo
                    terrae Fogaras iudici curiae et consiliario regiae maiestatis etc. ac supremo
                    regni Hungariae capitaneo etc. domino et amico observandissimo.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
